summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and East Fifty-seventh Street from Latona Avenue to Kenwood Place et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 20121, creating Local Improvement District No. 1946 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
